<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM4.5.9">
<l>pāvamu maṟamum vīṭu miṉpamun tuṉpan tāṉum</l>
<l>kōvamu maruḷu mallāk kuṇaṅkaḷu māya ventai</l>
<l>mūvari leṅkaḷ mūrtti yivaṉeṉa muṉiva rōṭu</l>
<l>tēvarvan tiṟaiñcum nāṅkūrt tirumaṇik kūṭat taṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Our father who, besides vice and virtue, disavowal and delight,</l>
<l>Misfortune and charity, rage and grace, became [all] qualities,</l>
<l>Is the one in Tirumaṇikkūṭam in Nāṅkūr where the gods worship,</l>
<l>Coming with sages who say, “Among the three, our god is he.”</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
